    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Drawings made by moving a drawing implement in one continuous line while looking at the subject of the drawing and not at the drawing itself. These are usually done as excercises in hand-eye coordination.</Note_Text>
